<subSubSection id="B6DC9EABFFE3FFB9FF3672CEDCDBFE42" pageId="82" pageNumber="95" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="FE79CD20FFE3FFB9FF3672CEDCDBFE42" blockId="82.[189,794,2025,2081]" lastBlockId="82.[830,1437,233,449]" pageId="82" pageNumber="95">
<emphasis id="CCB21132FFE3FFB9FF3672CED954F782" bold="true" box="[189,300,2025,2049]" pageId="82" pageNumber="95">Comment</emphasis>
: A re-examination of the type material of 
<taxonomicName id="39C6B6A3FFE3FFB9FF367D2DD966F7A2" authorityName="CAMERON" authorityYear="1939" box="[189,286,2057,2081]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Tetrabothrus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="82" pageNumber="95" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="bicolor">
<emphasis id="CCB21132FFE3FFB9FF367D2DD966F7A2" box="[189,286,2057,2081]" italics="true" pageId="82" pageNumber="95">T. bicolor</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="39C6B6A3FFE3FFB9FEEC7D2DD9A7F7A2" authorityName="PACE" authorityYear="2012" box="[359,479,2057,2081]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Tetrabothrus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="82" pageNumber="95" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="chinensis">
<emphasis id="CCB21132FFE3FFB9FEEC7D2DD9A7F7A2" box="[359,479,2057,2081]" italics="true" pageId="82" pageNumber="95">T. chinensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
revealed that both names refer to the same species; hence the synonymy proposed above. The aedeagi of the 
<typeStatus id="217D7382FFE3FFB9FBC4742EDCC8FEA2" box="[1103,1200,265,289]" pageId="82" pageNumber="95">lectotype</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName id="39C6B6A3FFE3FFB9FB47742DDD57FEA2" authorityName="CAMERON" authorityYear="1939" box="[1228,1327,265,289]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Tetrabothrus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="82" pageNumber="95" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="bicolor">
<emphasis id="CCB21132FFE3FFB9FB47742DDD57FEA2" box="[1228,1327,265,289]" italics="true" pageId="82" pageNumber="95">T. bicolor</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and of the 
<typeStatus id="217D7382FFE3FFB9FCB5740EDBE4FEC2" box="[830,924,297,321]" pageId="82" pageNumber="95">holotype</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName id="39C6B6A3FFE3FFB9FC4F740DDC44FEC2" authorityName="PACE" authorityYear="2012" box="[964,1084,297,321]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Tetrabothrus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="82" pageNumber="95" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="chinensis">
<emphasis id="CCB21132FFE3FFB9FC4F740DDC44FEC2" box="[964,1084,297,321]" italics="true" pageId="82" pageNumber="95">T. chinensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
are identical (see 
<bibRefCitation id="9A57B0D1FFE3FFB9FA89740EDDE1FEC2" author="ASSING, V." box="[1282,1433,297,321]" pageId="82" pageNumber="95" pagination="1257 - 1282" refId="ref76789" refString="ASSING, V. 2015 d: On the Lomechusini fauna of Vietnam (Coleoptera: Staphylinidae: Aleocharinae). - Linzer Biologische Beitrage 47 (2): 1257 - 1282." type="journal article" year="2015">ASSING 2015d</bibRefCitation>
: figures 31–32 and 
<bibRefCitation id="9A57B0D1FFE3FFB9FBAE746EDCDAFEE2" author="PACE, R." box="[1061,1186,329,353]" pageId="82" pageNumber="95" pagination="77 - 102" refId="ref78018" refString="PACE, R. 2012 a: Biodiversita delle Aleocharinae della Cina: Lomechusini e Thamiaraeini (Coleoptera, Staphylinidae). - Beitrage zur Entomologie, Keltern 62 (1): 77 - 102." type="journal article" year="2012">PACE 2012a</bibRefCitation>
: figures 20–21). The species is currently known from three localities in 
<collectingCountry id="86D18DB0FFE3FFB9FAC6744DDDE0FE02" box="[1357,1432,362,385]" name="Myanmar" pageId="82" pageNumber="95">Burma</collectingCountry>
, North 
<collectingCountry id="86D18DB0FFE3FFB9FC1B74AEDB96FE22" box="[912,1006,393,417]" name="Vietnam" pageId="82" pageNumber="95">Vietnam</collectingCountry>
, and 
<collectingCountry id="86D18DB0FFE3FFB9FBB174AEDC03FE22" box="[1082,1147,393,417]" name="China" pageId="82" pageNumber="95">China</collectingCountry>
(border region between 
<collectingRegion id="3C0203C2FFE3FFB9FCB4748EDBEDFE42" box="[831,917,425,449]" country="China" name="Shaanxi" pageId="82" pageNumber="95">Shaanxi</collectingRegion>
, 
<collectingRegion id="3C0203C2FFE3FFB9FC2B748EDC62FE42" box="[928,1050,425,449]" country="China" name="Chongqing" pageId="82" pageNumber="95">Chongqing</collectingRegion>
, and 
<collectingRegion id="3C0203C2FFE3FFB9FBDA748EDCEFFE42" box="[1105,1175,425,449]" country="China" name="Hubei" pageId="82" pageNumber="95">Hubei</collectingRegion>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
